ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都食左一年藥 頂住<br />\n<br />\n會唔會唔想同人講自己有情緒問題 （我會）</blockquote><br />\n朋友會知，同學就唔會刻意講，但問到我都唔會介意講"},{"pid":"e26223a4672ac1ea0caf196f28c1948728838ca4","tid":533620,"uid":162021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會成日喊</blockquote><br />\n以前會，依家食藥食到唔識喊</blockquote>有睇過好多連登既情緒病post <br />\n點解食完藥咁辛苦仲要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為唔食自己控制唔到自己啲思想同行為"},{"pid":"f917b8189a9dab065d5f410ac2be5fc92b7cfe8f","tid":533620,"uid":156854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:52:30.000Z","msg":"我都同你差唔多<br />\n我都食緊藥<br />\n而家好番好多<br />\n<br />\n你食邊隻?<br />\n咩誘發情緒病？"},{"pid":"2ec46588d3b138d27ac8c13e4ab08dbd7cc63bc8","tid":533620,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"有冇白卡?"},{"pid":"f7852cc3c2de634d03af51c57065c59af7098957","tid":533620,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:53:40.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n很多同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n按時吃藥 準時睡覺<br />\n照顧好自己 不要讓家裡人擔心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179fb4f559984b5f2c77bc54b9e57d7ee6ccec6f","tid":533620,"uid":156854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:55:22.000Z","msg":"你d藥幾多錢?"},{"pid":"2e91cdecaf4c2a6e6634764c8abcd768302a7ddf","tid":533620,"uid":162021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":